<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Berkeley Public Schools Fund, <%= @user.first_name %>!</h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully signed up to bpsf-staging.herokuapp.com,
      your login email is: <%= @user.email %>.
    </p>
    <p>Your account will need approval from the other admins first before you can perform administrator functions. You will be notified when they have approved your account.</p>
    <p>
      To login to the site, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for joining and have a great day!</p>
  <script type="text/javascript">
    if (<%= @user.type == "Admin" %>) {
      document.getElementById("admin").show()
    }
  </script>
  </body>
</html>